==English==

===Noun===
'''[[square]] [[metre]]''' (''UK spelling''; ''plural'' [[square metres]])
#[[Standard]] [[unit]] of [[area]], symbol m<sup>2</sup>, equal to the area of a square whose sides are one [[metre]] long.

